OL,3,CSNP faces last-minute pleas ahead of
OL,4,Cfinal Budget before election
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government will deliver
OL,7,Fits final Budget on Tuesday ahead of
OL,8,Fthe Holyrood election in May.
OL,10,FFinance Secretary Shona Robison will
OL,11,Fset out her tax and spending plans in
OL,12,FParliament at 2.20pm.
OL,14,FIt is expected to pass following
OL,15,FLabour's plans to abstain on the vote
OL,16,Fwhich will take place next month.
OL,18,FAhead of Tuesday's announcement,
OL,19,Fpolitical parties, charities and
OL,20,Fbusiness leaders made last-minute
OL,21,Fpleas to the SNP.
