OL,3,CSNP faces last-minute pleas ahead of
OL,4,Cfinal Budget before election
OL,6,FThe Conservatives urged the Government
OL,7,Fto cut income tax and slash the
OL,8,Fcountry's rising welfare bill, while
OL,9,Fthe Greens called for the expansion of
OL,10,Ffree bus travel, free school meals and
OL,11,Ffree childcare.
OL,13,FThe Lib Dems said they wanted to see a
OL,14,Fbetter funding settlement for colleges
OL,15,Fand councils along with a "fair deal"
OL,16,Ffor island communities.
OL,18,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,19,Fpreviously announced his party would
OL,20,Fabstain on the Budget vote,
OL,21,Feffectively allowing it to pass.
