OL,6,FIt comes amid increasingly strained
OL,7,Fpublic finances. Scotland's Auditor
OL,8,FGeneral warned the country faces a
OL,9,Fnear #5 billion funding shortfall by
OL,10,Fthe end of the decade.
OL,12,FThe Federation of Small Businesses
OL,13,Furged the Government to take action on
OL,14,Fplanned business rate rises to protect
OL,15,Findustries.
OL,17,FThe industry body said the country's
OL,18,Fgrowing tax burden has now overtaken
OL,19,Fstaffing as the single biggest factor
OL,20,Fdriving the "cost crisis" facing firms.
