OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Child Poverty Action
OL,7,FGroup called for the around #155
OL,8,Fmillion Scottish ministers could save
OL,9,Fas a result of the UK Government
OL,10,Fending the two-child benefit cap to
OL,11,Fstay in the social security budget.
OL,12,FThe charity called for the Scottish
OL,13,Fchild payment to be increased.
OL,15,FHowever, the Scottish Tories urged the
OL,16,FFinance Secretary to slash the welfare
OL,17,Fbudget, describing it as "out of
OL,18,Fcontrol".
