OL,6,FRussell Findlay, the party's leader,
OL,7,Fsaid ahead of the Budget: "Scottish
OL,8,Fhouseholds and businesses are
OL,9,Fstruggling after years of rising bills
OL,10,Funder the SNP Government.
OL,12,F"It is absolutely critical that John
OL,13,FSwinney starts listening and gives
OL,14,Fpeople a much-needed break.
OL,16,F"SNP stealth taxes have dragged
OL,17,Fhundreds of thousands of middle-
OL,18,Fearning Scots into higher tax bands,
OL,19,Fat the same time as their household
OL,20,Fbills have soared.
