OL,6,F"And many businesses across the
OL,7,Fcountry are on the brink. The SNP must
OL,8,Fditch their catastrophic business
OL,9,Frates revaluation and provide the
OL,10,Frelief they've denied hospitality
OL,11,Ffirms for years."
