OL,6,FMr Sarwar said the First Minister was
OL,7,F"taking the public for fools by
OL,8,Fpretending this SNP Government's 19th
OL,9,Fbudget will deliver anything other
OL,10,Fthan more of the same".
OL,12,FHe added: "John Swinney and the SNP
OL,13,Fcannot be trusted with a third decade
OL,14,Fin power and another five budgets to
OL,15,Fdamage Scotland's services."
OL,17,FThe First Minister said on Monday that
OL,18,Fdespite Labour's plans to abstain, he
OL,19,Fwould still "work very hard" to secure
OL,20,Fthe backing of other parties.
