OL,6,FHe said he was still keen to "work
OL,7,Fwith others" and "create common
OL,8,Fground" around the proposals.
OL,10,FMr Swinney said the Budget for 2026-27
OL,11,Fwould be focused on helping families
OL,12,Fstruggling with the cost-of-living
OL,13,Fcrisis, as well providing "strong
OL,14,Finvestment" for the NHS.
OL,16,FHere, the SNP leader said, he hoped
OL,17,Fthe Budget could help build on what he
OL,18,Finsisted was "significant progress" by
OL,19,Fthe NHS to tackle long waiting times
OL,20,Fthat have built up since the Covid
OL,21,Fpandemic.
